{"tid":1793784,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"（（巴打求救））想讀物理治療，做物理治療師，可以點做？","createTime":"2019-12-22T15:43:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-28T06:52:11.000Z","uid":256464,"like":0,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"46f088bb54fe041e33516b52a367d999d5e3a23a","tid":1793784,"uid":256464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T15:43:51.000Z","msg":"小弟以前讀 top up degree major finance .雖然讀讀下覺得無興趣，但都叫勉強畢到業.<br />\n因為本身一直喜歡健身，所以做左freelance健身教練.除左教人健身增肌，都有幫人做康復運動，漸漸對物理治療開始感興趣，買左啲相關書籍睇.發現自己對物理治療很感興趣，想成為一名註冊物理治療師.<br />\n想求教各位巴打，我可以點樣達成呢個目標，可以點做？<br />\nBtw,小弟做左小小資料收集知道香港好似得poly有得讀，可以試報poly 既物理治療master，但要大學有讀過解剖等課程，但小弟無<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，我可以點做，有無巴打有其他建議？跪求建議<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73fb18f8a31cb914dd98a405ef12bf42700d3d86","tid":1793784,"uid":302752,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T16:12:55.000Z","msg":"東大、OU 你直接讀master嘅話都會唔夠實習時數 攞唔到牌"},{"pid":"5c679d564cb2effe9a4499f8267104427355096a","tid":1793784,"uid":34525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T16:29:10.000Z","msg":"東大"},{"pid":"2e44dca31eacccf1c9a7d30afeb8ae4854d22541","tid":1793784,"uid":244781,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T16:40:18.000Z","msg":"Poly master年年一班phd,外國名校，護士爭，一定唔收你，東大都可能有d機會"},{"pid":"12ac27d149eb159dd385c9bee195f1ba31c6a9d6","tid":1793784,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T18:14:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9c5370b6489ea35a3fcec32661f3711fbdb3a58","tid":1793784,"uid":201669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T18:44:12.000Z","msg":"東大<br />\n<br />\n利申 東大PT女神"},{"pid":"511f35fce4018adf1aea06bddfa6c632596d6911","tid":1793784,"uid":256464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2e44dca31eacccf1c9a7d30afeb8ae4854d22541","tid":1793784,"uid":244781